23/06/2004
In other news, Macedonian Defence Minister Vlado Buckovski is at NATO headquarters in Brussels, seeking to boost support for the country's membership bid ahead of next week's summit in Istanbul. 
The Turkish Parliament issued a declaration of support Tuesday for the three Adriatic Charter countries -- Albania, Croatia and Macedonia. 
(Utrinski Vesnik - 23/06/04; A1 TV, Makfax - 22/06/04)
